WEBVTT

00:07:59.228 --> 00:08:00.983
that hyperinflated the bubble

00:08:00.983 --> 00:08:04.631
and produced the economic crisis.

00:08:04.631 --> 00:08:09.482
By 2006, half of all the loans called subprime

00:08:09.482 --> 00:08:11.508
were also liar's loans.

00:08:11.508 --> 00:08:14.793
They're not mutually exclusive, it's just that together,

00:08:14.793 --> 00:08:17.233
they're the most toxic combination

00:08:17.233 --> 00:08:19.093
you can possibly imagine.

00:08:19.093 --> 00:08:22.847
By 2006, 40 percent of all the loans

00:08:22.847 --> 00:08:25.464
made that year, all the home loans made that year,

00:08:25.464 --> 00:08:28.186
were liar's loans,

00:08:28.186 --> 00:08:29.497
40 percent.

00:08:29.497 --> 00:08:32.201
And this is despite a warning